{"tid":993093,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[無得救，等古天樂打救] 2019本地無咁主流音樂討論","createTime":"2019-01-23T16:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T20:47:18.000Z","uid":186882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b042981e53209b0590bacb75700fd5bdb4591869","tid":993093,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"本來舊年過咗去， 應該票選下舊年有邊10 首歌精選<br />\n但我自己都掛住打機， 又無咩人幫手推post<br />\n個舊post就由佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我自己聽開既音樂人都無放棄過創作<br />\n我覺得始終都想連登仔有多d時間同機會留意下<br />\n香港其實唔缺音樂人， 都唔缺音樂平台<br />\n缺乏既係聽眾， 香港市場太細<br />\n<br />\n希望間中有人幫下手推呢個post"},{"pid":"a8c8d7dd54668cabec3c75e9ba2322f8ca0056fc","tid":993093,"uid":186882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"Per se今年既project唔係出碟， 而係出月曆<br />\n而個月曆入面有qr code,  如果出新歌就可以優先download新歌<br />\n但你無比錢買日曆呢， 都係遲下去翻各大平台就會聽到<br />\n<br />\n當然啦， 比錢買月曆其實只係純粹儲同埋支持下佢地。 <br />\n其實cd無意義， 反正你真金白銀買隻碟<br />\n最後味又係dup翻落電話度用電話聽<br />\n倒不如直接買個art work<br />\n上網d/l正版唔使哂時間dup碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vCzogbzbO88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvCzogbzbO88&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=2f4df5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vCzogbzbO88</a>"},{"pid":"825327d4c34308f7c83bfed0f88f60b361d2c039","tid":993093,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"環球簽dusty bottle,  商業上未必係最佳收購<br />\n但對推動樂壇多元化絕對係一個好好既收購<br />\n佢地玩groove可以話係爐火純青<br />\n不論自己歌以至cover歌都非常襟聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X4KhZlx2J0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX4KhZlx2J0w&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ea0dc4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X4KhZlx2J0w</a><br />\n<br />\n而唔同歌唔同vocal,  雖然只係缺女vocal下既權宜之計<br />\n但都滿足到佢地玩音樂溝下女集下郵既慾望<br />\n希望呢個模式keep得住， 事實上sophy唱唔到this shit raw,  shimica唱唔到don't you know.<br />\n用唔同vocal,  佢地既groove就更多元化"},{"pid":"b65e8b4cf3c208b41af576233cb5d4ba94af279b","tid":993093,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:41:32.000Z","msg":"2018 年hiphop界撈得最撚掂， 一定係米奇老味<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZQzhAXk-jQM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZQzhAXk-jQM&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=02a4b0b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZQzhAXk-jQM</a><br />\n食住當年豪宅東個勢狂出新歌狂開show<br />\n但新歌真係做唔翻&lt;黑社會主義好&gt;呢隻天碟咁大膽<br />\n所以其實我覺得回塘回得幾明顯<br />\n無計， 以香港政治環境<br />\n&lt;黑社會主義好&gt;好快變做禁碟， 奶油神被人捉上洗頭艇係遲早嘅事"},{"pid":"a0d24b8167412d8971ef93480d678c843beb3e07","tid":993093,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33006dd1748914856b510aa0171a903de39fecd","tid":993093,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"JB都算係本地hiphop 界既raising star,  首潮共好撚高view (以本土hiphop計算係咁) <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fNtqH2kcvF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfNtqH2kcvF8&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6e77ffa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fNtqH2kcvF8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jot0ev7VPMs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJot0ev7VPMs&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d85acef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jot0ev7VPMs</a><br />\n<br />\n唔撚知點解好似大陸馬拉呢堆簡體字地區好似好撚buy,  有無人解釋到"},{"pid":"906037f5d5780008091658abda26e7f91e98b9a8","tid":993093,"uid":138689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci